  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "> \ud83e\udd16 This PR was written by Coder Agent on behalf of Danielle Maywood \ud83e\udd16\n\nThe `StreamingCodeFence` play test used `findByText` to look for text inside a `<diffs-container>` web component whose content lives in Shadow DOM. `testing-library` queries can't reach into Shadow DOM, so the assertion timed out non-deterministically.\n\nSwitches to `querySelector` for the web component element wrapped in `waitFor`, which correctly asserts the code fence was parsed into a FileViewer rather than rendered as raw backtick text.",
